message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with signal processing and audio analysis. cs.CL is also likely as it deals with natural language processing and speech recognition, which can be related to audio event detection. cs.LG is another possible category as it deals with machine learning and classification, which are used in the proposed framework. cs.CV is also possible as it deals with computer vision and image/signal processing, which can be related to audio analysis. cs.MM is another possible category as it deals with multimedia analysis and processing, which is the application domain of the proposed framework.
